    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/a01ec1705dd27793abaef25d92231c1c.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><strong>TINY ATOLLS</strong>是一款极简主义的建筑策略游戏<br>扩展到五彩缤纷的岛屿，解锁新地块并完成任务！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/53542a54973cc76995168576645b8d39.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/4a4e22337ab5959ebe35295774971b2e.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><strong>TINY ATOLLS</strong> 就是要在类型和颜色之间建立正确的联系。<br>您建立的连接越多，分数就越高，您可以放置的瓷砖就越多。<br>除了常规图块之外，您还可以使用一组卡片工具来帮助您扩展您的小型定居点。<br>解决任务和赚取积分将使您能够选择探索其他岛屿和改造景观所需的正确工具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/19bc65a674c34a0a3a931e44bc3932a7.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有些任务很特殊，会要求放置特定的地块，以建造具有各种新机制的独特建筑。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.poster.avif?t=1744459461\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.webm?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/c04483fb23828843413ea3c00c7cd13f.mp4?t=1744459461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2246640/extras/8ad63a96ed86ab0c7964e0a37933dbaa.avif?t=1744459461\" width=615 height=100 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>程序生成的岛屿<br></li><li>任务和可解锁的方块<br></li><li>美丽、鲜艳的色彩<br></li><li>模块化平铺<br></li><li>平静舒适的氛围<br></li><li>在线排行榜</li></ul>",
